{"tid":1220391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(反送中) 日本 2,500 人澀谷集會, 高歌《海闊天空》支持香港人","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T14:58:12.000Z","uid":134071,"like":105,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e196fa228363eaeaa8c75baf9cec1b9a8f13bc","tid":1220391,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-2-500-%E4%BA%BA%E6%BE%80%E8%B0%B7%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E9%AB%98%E6%AD%8C-%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%A9%BA-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA/?fbclid=IwAR0ZqEEqiUzEJIX-2ISytOzE3IrP3goOuLgihUbG0wBWdx3i7vcn0ueUt6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-2-500-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25BE%2580%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ZqEEqiUzEJIX-2ISytOzE3IrP3goOuLgihUbG0wBWdx3i7vcn0ueUt6s&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=42025aae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-2-500-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25BE%2580%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2597%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ZqEEqiUzEJIX-2ISytOzE3IrP3goOuLgihUbG0wBWdx3i7vcn0ueUt6s&h=7e62e7e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-2-500-%E4%BA%BA%E6%BE%80%E8%B0%B7%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E9%AB%98%E6%AD%8C-%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%A9%BA-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA/?fbclid=IwAR0ZqEEqiUzEJIX-2ISytOzE3IrP3goOuLgihUbG0wBWdx3i7vcn0ueUt6s</a></span><br />\n<br />\n【反送中】日本 2,500 人澀谷集會 高歌《海闊天空》支持香港人<br />\n<br />\n2019/6/14 &mdash; 10:27<br />\n<br />\n日本澀谷昨日約 2,500 人舉行反送中集會。參加者除日本人和香港人外，亦有不少台灣人。他們高叫「香港加油」的口號，又唱《海闊天空》，希望表達與港人連成一線的意願。<br />\n<br />\n昨夜集會於晚上 9 點至 10 點在東京澀谷忠犬八公像前廣場舉行。發起人為前日本社運團體 SEALDs 成員、今年 27 歲的研究院生元山仁士郎。他在 2014 年傘運後，曾多次與香港社運界交流。集會目的在與香港人共同進退，抗議香港政府強行通過修例，以及警察濫權。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter 上，日本人以 #TOKYOantiELAB 連結反送中消息。透過社交網絡，主辦方表示聚集到約 2,500 人，當中約有三分一為香港留學生，此外亦有許多日本人，以至台灣人。集會人士以日語、國語、廣東話高叫「香港加油」，並一齊唱 Beyond 的《海闊天空》。有人在高舉的標語上直接使用「反送中」一詞。他們呼籲日本民眾支持香港人，共同站起來為人權、民主戰鬥，又批評香港警察過度使用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n元山表示，「在香港被催淚彈和橡膠子彈攻擊的，與我們同樣都是學生。我們在這裡有集會自由、言論自由，香港現在也為這些自由戰鬥。」<br />\n<br />\n同日傍晚，元山仁士郎又與約 300 人前往東京的香港商務及經濟發展局辦事處，亦舉行抗議集會，舉起「守護香港自由」等標語，為香港的抗爭者吶喊加油。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：每日新聞、朝日新聞"},{"pid":"7ac1b5dc84f910bb709d6f575e080e3a3eb40ed7","tid":1220391,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb86b99b434f7b1b43a4e45aac72b8ac536edbc","tid":1220391,"uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:00:15.000Z","msg":"新聞片段<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Af1Z8PHPIq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAf1Z8PHPIq0&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=a772de13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Af1Z8PHPIq0</a>"},{"pid":"1282059adf20e42f17f7f1ea4dbe7a8e937b7188","tid":1220391,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c4ced5d20c2bf68b4af7417c754dc1d1